g.title: j185389989
g.text: Quincy came to talk to me

g.title: j1774801472
g.text: I just... wanted to say sorry, Lettie. That's all.

g.title: j3088472410
g.text: I... well. I have feelings for you.

g.title: j3697981924
g.text: JAJA Sí, that's what he said
I didn't believe him at first
But now I'm impressed that you've got him working for you, huh?

g.title: j2015798562
g.text: You just want to apologize and I'm making it hard for you

g.title: j584608100
g.text: And it didn't go so well, did it?
Hard to admit that I miss you

g.title: j2226962620
g.text: You kept this to yourself the whole time?

g.title: j4121139439
g.text: He *also* said you wanted to give things a shot with me

g.title: j2321116145
g.text: You want to give this another try?

g.title: j2955670583
g.text: Sometimes, I want to smack you
This is one of those times

g.title: j2434285118
g.text: Let's get on with it, then
